BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, April 10 (XINHUA) -- M. J. Qhobela, 
minister of foreign affairs of the Kingdom of Lesotho arrived 
here this afternoon for a week-long visit to China as guest of 
his Chinese counterpart Qian Qichen . 
  It is learned that Qhobela's visit is aimed at promoting 
bilateral relations and studying China's reform and opening-up. 

